134
00:12:14,679 --> 00:12:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] To su izraženi.

135
00:12:16,159 --> 00:12:18,200
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, slobodno, naravno, pa to je glavoposto.

136
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:20,299
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, udravljame motor, skuferon,

137
00:12:20,299 --> 00:12:22,259
[SPEAKER_00] na Harley-Davidson neki.

138
00:12:22,259 --> 00:12:25,460
[SPEAKER_01] I koji si zakričak i zvukov iz toga.

139
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:26,899
[SPEAKER_00] Dobio sam ono po glavi.

140
00:12:26,899 --> 00:12:28,960
[SPEAKER_01] Kao, ne, ne, ne, kao, dobro ništa.

141
00:12:29,039 --> 00:12:30,179
[SPEAKER_01] Lupa foro, zaboravaj.

142
00:12:30,179 --> 00:12:32,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ne, ne, ne, ne, ne idem dalje, ne, ne idem dalje.

143
00:12:32,820 --> 00:12:33,700
[SPEAKER_00] Slobodno, slobodno.

144
00:12:33,700 --> 00:12:35,220
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, sad kad pogledaš u nas,

145
00:12:35,220 --> 00:12:36,519
[SPEAKER_00] kad pogledaš moramo sam išli.

146
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:36,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da, okej.

147
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:38,399
[SPEAKER_00] Meni to učinje ne smetam.

148
00:12:38,399 --> 00:12:38,720
[SPEAKER_00] Zašto?

149
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:42,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer drugačiji dobiješ, Bogu dobiješ drugačiji inetiteta onoga što jesi.

150
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,080
[SPEAKER_00] Ali je zanimljiva jedna stvar.

151
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:49,399
[SPEAKER_00] Moj otac je imao šednog brata, koji bi je stariji, i njega je udrla u to.

152
00:12:49,399 --> 00:12:51,759
[SPEAKER_00] Baš tu u blizini i pogineo je.

153
00:12:51,759 --> 00:12:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] I ono, kad sad gledaš malo duhovnu neku perspektivu, svega toga viš, ono, koliko imam prste iza toga, znaš.

154
00:12:58,899 --> 00:13:11,899
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon toga, a morat ćete, kao sam reka, nakon svi tih ludila nekakve u svog života, ta nekakva delikvencija, nekakva kriva društva, nestrah od neznam čega i tako dalje.

155
00:13:11,899 --> 00:13:17,679
[SPEAKER_00] Puno neuspjeha u životu iz moje perspektive.

156
00:13:17,679 --> 00:13:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, već 7. i 8. razred, ja jednostavno padam baš ono, duboko, daleko od svega.

157
00:13:23,980 --> 00:13:25,419
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav si bio u školi?

158
00:13:25,419 --> 00:13:26,919
[SPEAKER_00] U školi.

159
00:13:26,919 --> 00:13:29,120
[SPEAKER_00] A u školi sam bio prosjećan.

160
00:13:29,120 --> 00:13:35,580
[SPEAKER_00] I ako će se svi, ono, reći da sam, da je za mene, da sam, ono, inteligentan i to, da mi nije nikad, ja nikad nisam učio.

161
00:13:35,580 --> 00:13:44,820
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam, ono, dobro, to ćemo kasnije, jav, da sam za njim popročita knjigu, ne sada, ne, kada sam išao u Bogoslovi, da sam za njim u trećem osnovne pročita Šegrota Hlapića, ali nevam pojma.

162
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:47,840
[SPEAKER_00] I sve do fakulteta, ono, da Bogoslovi.

163
00:13:47,840 --> 00:13:49,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da si znao da će biti film, ne bi ni to, jel da?

164
00:13:49,740 --> 00:14:12,340
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon toga, već sve mi osmi razred, ja je jako duboko padan, te obsesivne milici me jednostavno pretjerano opterećuju i ja dolazim do faze nekakvog bunjela usunutar sebe i, ono, već razmišljam samo o bojstvu i da je to prekinen.

165
00:14:12,679 --> 00:14:15,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ono, tako, sad sam imao, ono, 3-14 godina.

166
00:14:15,039 --> 00:14:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] Niko to nije znao?

167
00:14:16,559 --> 00:14:28,580
[SPEAKER_00] Niko to nije znao, čak se svića na moment je bilo, ono, da me, ono, na nekom, s mom stanjem šoka, ovoga, u svojoj sobi nisam ima ništa oštrosim kad sam ide, pa sam išao sebi, ono, prezatvojene.

168
00:14:28,580 --> 00:14:41,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, prestrašno, prestrašno, ali, ja kad sam sad, kad sad pogledam stvari, ono, vidim da sam neke stvari, ono, prošao, eto, nekad i s razlogom, ono, da danas tako me mogu pomoći.

169
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:49,100
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, uglavnom, i jedna sam, došao sam do baš jedne faze, gdje sam puka, gdje nisam više moga, nisam to priznao.

170
00:14:49,100 --> 00:14:51,200
[SPEAKER_00] I, vjerojatno, mi je to spazilo život.

171
00:14:51,200 --> 00:14:52,519
[SPEAKER_01] Došao si roditeljima, stilio?

172
00:14:52,519 --> 00:14:54,840
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, došao sam. I, ono, oni su bili u šoku.

173
00:14:54,840 --> 00:15:03,419
[SPEAKER_00] Neljavetno je, koliko zapravo, ja sam to toliko upao, na kraju su mi diagnosticirali, mi je obsesivno kompoziran, mi je poremeće, ono, teški i nekakav.

174
00:15:03,419 --> 00:15:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] Ja bi, ono, ne znam, ono, sad trebam, prema šta bi šaleće, ono, sve te rituale obalja.

175
00:15:09,559 --> 00:15:12,960
[SPEAKER_00] Ono, svaki dan bi čitao, ono, sve novine.

176
00:15:12,960 --> 00:15:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uglavnom, prestrašno. Razvio sam totalno nekakvu, nekakav svoj svijet, ono, bio sam udaljen.

177
00:15:18,500 --> 00:15:20,840
[SPEAKER_01] To je sve gonjeno nekim strahom u pozadini i to je.

178
00:15:20,840 --> 00:15:26,399
[SPEAKER_00] Da, religijski strah, na kraju je bio, kad pogled, zbog ubitka strice.

179
00:15:26,399 --> 00:15:28,179
[SPEAKER_01] A kje bi značilo religijski strah?

180
00:15:28,179 --> 00:15:29,879
[SPEAKER_00] Strah od, od Boga.

181
00:15:29,879 --> 00:15:30,539
[SPEAKER_01] A, ok.

182
00:15:30,539 --> 00:15:32,639
[SPEAKER_00] I to je nekakva nesigurnost.

183
00:15:32,639 --> 00:15:33,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ok.

184
00:15:34,059 --> 00:15:35,259
[SPEAKER_00] I to je bilo prestrašno.

185
00:15:35,259 --> 00:15:36,740
[SPEAKER_00] To je baš bilo prestrašno.

186
00:15:36,740 --> 00:15:38,779
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam doslovno razvio sustave brojeva.

187
00:15:38,779 --> 00:15:42,639
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, se gleda mi film 23 ikada.

188
00:15:43,139 --> 00:15:51,340
[SPEAKER_00] To je baš film o tome, to je ono, trilere, girao, ono, ali nakon, nakon nešto sam ja doživio svome život.

189
00:15:51,340 --> 00:15:52,960
[SPEAKER_00] Naravno nisam koga ubio, taj čovjek nekak nekako ubio.

190
00:15:52,960 --> 00:15:55,200
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, daj mi sam, sad ću samo mrvu skrenuti.

191
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:55,559
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš.

192
00:15:55,559 --> 00:16:05,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj bi rekao, ne, u stvari, pardon, neću sad uči, ti još sam reći, kaj bi preporučio ljudima u toj fazi, ti si rekao priznao sam.

193
00:16:05,519 --> 00:16:06,960
[SPEAKER_01] To je očito bilo bitno.

194
00:16:06,960 --> 00:16:10,779
[SPEAKER_01] Kaj bi preporučio nekom ko se može sad nalazi u tome, priznaš to prije?

195
00:16:10,779 --> 00:16:11,259
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

196
00:16:12,860 --> 00:16:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] Neverovatno je koliko Bog dopusti zapravo da ja kroz ispovedi saznam za takve ljude.

197
00:16:17,360 --> 00:16:21,179
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja često čujem takve stvari zato se to je pitan, prepostavim da se dosta ljudi s tim bore.

198
00:16:21,179 --> 00:16:25,919
[SPEAKER_00] Krene od prazna vjera, krene od nekakvih prazna vjera, krene od nekakvih prazna vjera, svi imamo nekakva prazna vjera.

199
00:16:25,919 --> 00:16:31,539
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš, ono, jesam ugasio peglu, pa se deset puta, jesam zaključava vrata, pa deset puta provjerava i tako dalje.

200
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:39,860
[SPEAKER_00] Svi krenemo od nećega takoga, ali kasnije se to mora stvarno pretvoriti u puno zbiljnije stvari, tako nekakve prisilne misli i tako dalje.

201
00:16:40,259 --> 00:16:44,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pogotovo neko ko želi se obratiti, želi se riješiti nekakvih grijeha i tako dalje.

202
00:16:44,460 --> 00:16:48,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ne znam, psovke ti padaju napoju. Ima tu stvarno teške, teške situacije.

203
00:16:48,039 --> 00:16:52,860
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam se sustrao baš ono, ja nisam bio u tom nekom, ja sam uvijek ima straglaći se nekome nešto došlo dogoditi.

204
00:16:52,860 --> 00:16:57,259
[SPEAKER_00] Ali, čak ne prema sebi, nego prema drugima.

205
00:16:57,259 --> 00:17:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] I ovoga, tako da sigurno šta prije to priznati, ima...

206
00:17:01,000 --> 00:17:03,600
[SPEAKER_01] To je zanimljivo. U stvari ti nije toliko do tebe, nego ti...

207
00:17:03,600 --> 00:17:05,059
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, verovatno, ne, verovatno.

208
00:17:05,400 --> 00:17:10,519
[SPEAKER_00] Jer, ovoga, važno je to priznati, jer šta prije, prije će se riješiti.

209
00:17:10,519 --> 00:17:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] I onda, znaš, često puta ljudi misle, ono, pogotovo je danas, mi se s tim susrećemo puno,

210
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudi misle da će tablete riješiti stvar. Neće.

211
00:17:17,779 --> 00:17:23,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam tada pio terapiju, ovoga, za moj uzrast, na kraju krajeva.

212
00:17:23,920 --> 00:17:26,880
[SPEAKER_00] I tablete nikada nisu riješile moj problem.

213
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:30,039
[SPEAKER_00] Znači, ja sam bilo s osmi razli, ja sam bilo na terapiji.

214
00:17:30,039 --> 00:17:32,599
[SPEAKER_00] Danas je to možda čak i normalno.

215
00:17:32,599 --> 00:17:36,039
[SPEAKER_00] puno djece i tako dalje, ali u moje vrijeme to nije bila normalno, naravno.

216
00:17:36,039 --> 00:17:38,319
[SPEAKER_01] A malo mjesto, svi znaju.

217
00:17:38,319 --> 00:17:40,000
[SPEAKER_00] Da, dobra, nije se to toliko znalo.

218
00:17:40,000 --> 00:17:42,299
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ovo niko ni ne znao, što sam prvi puji spričio.

219
00:17:42,299 --> 00:17:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je vani.

220
00:17:43,940 --> 00:17:47,420
[SPEAKER_00] Sad je vani. Ne, ne, došli smrti, smaćemo i do kraja, i to je to.

221
00:17:47,420 --> 00:17:49,900
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ono, već sam,

222
00:17:49,900 --> 00:17:52,059
[SPEAKER_00] meni su tablete puno pomogle u kontekstu

223
00:17:52,059 --> 00:17:53,859
[SPEAKER_00] da bi one mene izvlačile

224
00:17:53,859 --> 00:17:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] iz tih stanja akcijoznosti

225
00:17:56,279 --> 00:17:57,980
[SPEAKER_00] i otvarali su mi prostor

226
00:17:57,980 --> 00:17:59,900
[SPEAKER_00] u mome danu da ja mogu živiti normalno.

227
00:18:00,359 --> 00:18:02,279
[SPEAKER_00] jer sam morao sam se boriti sam s tim

228
00:18:02,279 --> 00:18:04,640
[SPEAKER_00] i ulazi tu sve veće rizike, naravno da se ništa neće dogoditi.

229
00:18:04,640 --> 00:18:06,160
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam kroz to zapravo

230
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,400
[SPEAKER_00] mora reći riješio tu stvar.

231
00:18:07,400 --> 00:18:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] Jer sam možda imao malo sreće, každje danas

232
00:18:10,039 --> 00:18:11,400
[SPEAKER_00] da je to OKP neizlječiv,

233
00:18:11,400 --> 00:18:14,019
[SPEAKER_00] ali ja u svom slučaju

234
00:18:14,019 --> 00:18:15,140
[SPEAKER_00] ga više ne primjećujem.

235
00:18:15,140 --> 00:18:18,359
[SPEAKER_00] Ali možda sam i prerasta.

236
00:18:18,359 --> 00:18:20,059
[SPEAKER_00] Možda sam baš imao malo sreće

237
00:18:20,059 --> 00:18:22,160
[SPEAKER_00] da je to bilo nekako djetico, pa su ti strahve

238
00:18:22,160 --> 00:18:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] postati toliko banalni kasnije.

239
00:18:24,079 --> 00:18:27,160
[SPEAKER_00] A znači svakako bih rekao

240
00:18:27,160 --> 00:18:29,500
[SPEAKER_01] izaći s tim i zatražiti neku pomoću.

241
00:18:29,500 --> 00:18:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] Da, jasno, svakako.

242
00:18:30,539 --> 00:18:32,259
[SPEAKER_00] Svakako jer

243
00:18:32,259 --> 00:18:35,500
[SPEAKER_00] to te vodi sigurno

244
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] samo ovojstvo, ako to ne prekeneš.

245
00:18:37,579 --> 00:18:39,220
[SPEAKER_00] Možda ne sad,

246
00:18:39,220 --> 00:18:40,960
[SPEAKER_00] ali za dvih godine, tri.

247
00:18:40,960 --> 00:18:42,799
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam bilo, to je robstvo.

248
00:18:42,799 --> 00:18:44,259
[SPEAKER_00] To je kuriš godinama robstvo.

249
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:45,640
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ono,

250
00:18:45,640 --> 00:18:47,599
[SPEAKER_00] to je baš frustrirajuće robstvo.

251
00:18:47,599 --> 00:18:49,099
[SPEAKER_00] I ovoga,

252
00:18:49,099 --> 00:18:50,559
[SPEAKER_00] i vije, naravno,

253
00:18:50,559 --> 00:18:53,099
[SPEAKER_00] djava to koristi da te drži negdje tamo

254
00:18:53,099 --> 00:18:53,759
[SPEAKER_00] ne želiš biti.

255
00:18:53,759 --> 00:18:54,740
[SPEAKER_00] Ne možeš ostvariti,

256
00:18:54,740 --> 00:18:55,640
[SPEAKER_00] nemaš ništa, razumiš.

257
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,160
[SPEAKER_00] I nakon toga,

258
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:58,000
[SPEAKER_00] znači, ja vam reći,

259
00:18:58,000 --> 00:18:59,039
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo osnova škola.

260
00:18:59,039 --> 00:18:59,640
[SPEAKER_00] Osmi razred.

261
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:01,079
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je, veći osmi razred.

262
00:19:01,079 --> 00:19:02,839
[SPEAKER_00] Ulazak u srednju školu.

263
00:19:02,839 --> 00:19:04,339
[SPEAKER_00] Znaš šta,

264
00:19:04,339 --> 00:19:06,240
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam dosta lišo prolazio

265
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:06,960
[SPEAKER_00] u osnovnoj školi.

266
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:09,660
[SPEAKER_00] Bila ta nekakva ekipa

267
00:19:09,660 --> 00:19:11,099
[SPEAKER_00] koja je uvijek bila gora malo od mene.

268
00:19:11,099 --> 00:19:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] Jedna sam dosta lišo prolazio.

269
00:19:13,220 --> 00:19:16,839
[SPEAKER_00] A nikad ne zaboravljati.

270
00:19:16,839 --> 00:19:19,660
[SPEAKER_00] Vesam poćeo moći vozim otvor u sve most.

271
00:19:19,660 --> 00:19:21,680
[SPEAKER_00] Sve šta ću ja,

272
00:19:21,680 --> 00:19:22,440
[SPEAKER_00] evo, iskreno,

273
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:23,660
[SPEAKER_00] sve šta ću ja izreći,

274
00:19:23,660 --> 00:19:25,900
[SPEAKER_00] ne želim da ljudi cvate

275
00:19:25,900 --> 00:19:26,680
[SPEAKER_00] kao neko hvaljenje,

276
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:26,900
[SPEAKER_00] nešto,

277
00:19:26,900 --> 00:19:28,680
[SPEAKER_00] ali pokušavam predoći situaciju

278
00:19:28,680 --> 00:19:30,240
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo kako je to sve.

279
00:19:30,240 --> 00:19:31,119
[SPEAKER_01] To je biti...

280
00:19:31,119 --> 00:19:32,619
[SPEAKER_01] E, da ne ispane samo naša.

281
00:19:32,619 --> 00:19:34,059
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš reći.

282
00:19:34,059 --> 00:19:34,960
[SPEAKER_01] Moraš reći najgore

283
00:19:34,960 --> 00:19:36,140
[SPEAKER_01] da bi su stvari pokazala.

284
00:19:36,140 --> 00:19:36,519
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da.

285
00:19:37,660 --> 00:19:39,119
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ono, već sam sve osnovno

286
00:19:39,119 --> 00:19:39,900
[SPEAKER_00] počeo vozim motor

287
00:19:39,900 --> 00:19:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] ovoga

288
00:19:40,900 --> 00:19:42,400
[SPEAKER_00] i, ono,

289
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,880
[SPEAKER_00] kad čača me ne vidi po cesti,

290
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:44,440
[SPEAKER_00] kad me vidi,

291
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:44,640
[SPEAKER_00] ona,

292
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:45,380
[SPEAKER_00] negdje,

293
00:19:45,380 --> 00:19:47,180
[SPEAKER_00] i nikad ne zaboravljati,

294
00:19:47,180 --> 00:19:47,640
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

295
00:19:47,640 --> 00:19:49,220
[SPEAKER_00] završetak ovog smo grazili,

296
00:19:49,220 --> 00:19:50,220
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

297
00:19:50,220 --> 00:19:50,819
[SPEAKER_00] danas, ono,

298
00:19:50,819 --> 00:19:51,940
[SPEAKER_00] djeci to puno pregovaraju,

299
00:19:51,940 --> 00:19:52,099
[SPEAKER_00] ono,

300
00:19:52,099 --> 00:19:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] mi smo desputa gori.

301
00:19:53,500 --> 00:19:54,339
[SPEAKER_00] Ono,

302
00:19:54,339 --> 00:19:55,539
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam zapalio gumu na motore

303
00:19:55,539 --> 00:19:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] svi škole.

304
00:19:56,000 --> 00:19:57,359
[SPEAKER_00] Tako.

305
00:19:57,359 --> 00:19:59,339
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo je tu situacija,

306
00:19:59,339 --> 00:19:59,940
[SPEAKER_00] milijardu.

307
